****************************Product Write Review Test Steps*************************************************

Product write review recommend product Yes test1
1. Go to development.ariat.com
2. Choose UK
3. Go to Accessories category
4. Choose glove product
5. Click on "write review"
6. Write a title, a description, set "Excellent" for star, click "Yes" for recommend
7. Set user nickname as "aila", "London" as city & email address "aila.bogasieru@gmail.com"
8. Press "post review" button


Product write review recommend product No test2
1. Go to development.ariat.com
2. Choose UK
3. Go to Accessories category
4. Choose glove product
5. Click on "write review"
6. Write a title, a description, set "Excellent" for star, click "No" for recommend
7. Set user nickname as "aila", "London" as city & email address "aila.bogasieru@gmail.com"
8. Press "post review" button
